      {
        "chunk_type": "body",
        "translations": {
          "en": "Al-Ḥasan ibn ʿAlī ibn Yaqṭīn wrote to al-ʿAbd al-Ṣāliḥ عليه السلام: “May a man perform the salat (prayer) while wearing an izār wrapped around himself over the qamīṣ?” So he wrote: “Yes.”",
